chore: configure knip to ignore papi descriptors and API surface types

- ignore .papi/** (auto-generated polkadot-api descriptors consumed via
  package.json alias, not direct imports)
- ignoreExportsUsedInFile for interface/type (API surface types used as
  return types and function signatures but never directly imported)

